    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The 500ft ASR Outdoor Paracord Rope in OD Green is a great multi-purpose rope for camping, hiking, survival, and all your outdoor activities. When reliability is essential, The ASR Outdoor Survival Paracord is a must-have addition to your survival kit or camping/hiking gear collection. This rope has a working load of 220lbs and a breaking point of 550lbs. It&#039;s 7 strands thick with a 5/32&quot; diameter. The olive drab green color of the rope is great for camouflage and stealth. Be sure to beef up your bug out bag with the ASR Outdoor Survival Paracord!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Paracord Mil-Spec Commercial Grade 550lb Type III Nylon Cord Rope Many Lengths</h2>\n  <p>The 500ft ASR Outdoor Paracord Rope in OD Green is a great multi-purpose rope for camping, hiking, survival, and all your outdoor activities.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>Length:</strong> 500ft Paracord Rope</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> OD Green</li>\n    <li><strong>Working Load:</strong> 220lbs</li>\n    <li><strong>Breaking Strength:</strong> 550lbs</li>\n    <li><strong>Construction:</strong> 7 Strand</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/camping_outdoors/cord/Paracord_parent.jpg\" alt=\"The 500ft ASR Outdoor Paracord Rope in OD Green is a great multi-purpose rope for camping, hiking, survival, and all your outdoor activities\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> DC-50-154</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 884101334628</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>When reliability is essential, The ASR Outdoor Survival Paracord is a must-have addition to your survival kit or camping/hiking gear collection. This rope has a working load of 220lbs and a breaking point of 550lbs. It&#039;s 7 strands thick with a 5/32&quot; diameter. The olive drab green color of the rope is great for camouflage and stealth.</p>\n  <p>Be sure to beef up your bug out bag with the ASR Outdoor Survival Paracord!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The 500ft ASR Outdoor Paracord Rope in OD Green is a great multi-purpose rope for camping, hiking, survival, and all your outdoor activities. When reliability is essential, The ASR Outdoor Survival Paracord is a must-have addition to your survival kit or camping/hiking gear collection. This rope has a working load of 220lbs and a breaking point of 550lbs. It's 7 strands thick with a 5/32\" diameter. The olive drab green color of the rope is great for camouflage and stealth. Be sure to beef up your bug out bag with the ASR Outdoor Survival Paracord!.",
